records.question: Total revenue by product
records.sql:
SELECT 
    p.productname,
    SUM(CAST(oi.quantity AS INT) * CAST(oi.unitprice AS DOUBLE)) AS total_revenue
FROM order_items oi
JOIN products p ON oi.productid = p.productid
GROUP BY p.productname
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;

records.question: Show me all products
records.sql:
SELECT 
    productid,
    productname,
    category,
    CAST(price AS DOUBLE) AS price,
    CAST(stockquantity AS INT) AS stock_quantity
FROM products;

records.question: Total revenue by product
records.sql:
SELECT
    p.productid,
    p.productname,
    p.category,
    SUM(CAST(oi.quantity AS INT) * CAST(oi.unitprice AS DOUBLE)) AS total_revenue
FROM
    products p
    JOIN order_items oi ON p.productid = oi.productid
GROUP BY
    p.productid,
    p.productname,
    p.category
ORDER BY
    total_revenue DESC;
